    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.title": "真空包裝特性",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.toc_title": "真空包裝特性",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.header_ref": "CH.09 — VACUUM PROPERTIES",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.title": "品牌与保養／維修信息",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.toc_title": "品牌与保養／維修信息",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.header_ref": "CH.10 — WARRANTY",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.1": "本機僅供家庭使用，請勿用於其他非設計用途。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.2": "請勿讓兒童玩耍本機或電源線。兒童、行動不便或認知受限人士應在成年人監督下使用。使用期間請留意兒童，避免意外發生。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.3": "小零件、真空袋可能造成窒息危險，請勿讓兒童接觸。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.4": "請勿在高濕高溫等環境使用本機。嚴禁在有易燃易爆氣體的環境中使用。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.5": "請確保電源電壓与機器銘牌標示一致。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.6": "機器工作時請勿離開。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.7": "密封完成後，密封區域溫度较高，請勿觸摸，以免燙傷。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.8": "使用後請切斷電源。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.9": "從電源插座上拔出插头時請手握插头拔出，請勿拉扯電源線。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.10": "請勿將主機或電源線浸入水中或其他液體中。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.11": "電源線需要直接插接符合安全規範的電源插座上。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.12": "如發现插头、電源線或主機損壞，請立即停止使用並聯繫製造商或授權維修點處理，請勿自行拆修。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.13": "電源線請勿懸掛於臺麵邊缘，以免兒童拉扯或意外絆倒。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.title": "警告 WARNING",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "請妥善保管本手册。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "本機無需添加任何潤滑劑，請勿使用有機溶劑清潔。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.3": "長時間不使用時，請勿扣上鎖扣，以免密封圈受壓變形。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.4": "請勿將本產品与生活垃圾一同丟棄，請根據您所在地區關於電子废棄物的法規進行回收或處置。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.title": "注意 CAUTION",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.3.item.1": "本產品適用於家庭食品保鮮用途。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.3.item.2": "首次使用前，請完整閱讀本說明書。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.3.item.3": "請保留購買憑證，以便享受保養／維修服務。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.3.title": "提示 NOTICE",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.section_title": "安全須知",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.1": "本機只適用於带有空氣通道紋路的真空袋。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.2": "對於带有尖點或棱角的物品，需用防刺穿片、紙巾等柔軟包材包裹棱角，以防刺破真空袋。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.3": "真空袋可用於加熱或微波炉加熱，但必須先在袋角剪開一個小口透氣。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.4": "用於儲存的真空袋可重復使用，但用於加熱或微波加熱時僅可使用一次。儲存過海鮮或油腻食品的真空袋不建議重復使用。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.5": "放置袋子時，袋口必須平整地跨過發熱器。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.6": "裝袋時，請務必在袋口和食物之間預留至少 2 inch（5 cm）的空間。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.7": "裝入液體、醬汁或带液體的食物時，請避免將真空袋袋口弄濕。建議裝入後將袋口擦乾，以免影響密封效果。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.8": "如果需要質地柔軟、含水分多的食物在包裝後保持形狀，可選擇冷凍後進行真空封裝。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.9": "勿在麵蓋上放置重物，有可能損壞機器。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.section_title": "產品及真空袋使用提示",
    "content.chapter.03-structure.page.page1.block.3.text": "工作結束後，發熱器溫度很高，請不要觸摸，以免燙傷！",
    "content.chapter.03-structure.page.page1.block.3.title": "提示",
    "content.chapter.03-structure.page.page1.section_title": "產品結構",
    "content.chapter.04-functions.page.page1.section_title": "產品功能",
    "content.chapter.05-specifications.page.page1.section_title": "技術參數",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.1.text": "6.1 如何使用切袋刀",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step1.text": "打開麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step2.text": "打開切袋刀架。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step3.text": "從卷袋上拉扯出所需長度的袋子。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step4.text": "將切袋刀移至最左或最右邊，再使刀架下壓著袋子。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step5.text": "將切袋刀下壓滑動劃過袋子，以進行整齊的切割。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.3.text": "6.2 如何使用密封功能",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.4.text": "**從卷袋中製作袋子並密封：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.step.step1.text": "按以上如何使用切袋刀製作出一個兩端開口的袋子。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.step.step2.text": "將袋子的一端開口平整放入真空腔內。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.step.step3.text": "關閉麵蓋，並將把手向下壓以鎖紧麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.step.step4.text": "點擊 [btn:Seal] 按鍵，並等待機器完成工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.6.text": "**單獨密封袋子：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.7.body.1.step.step1.text": "將袋子放入需要封裝的物品，並將袋口放入真空腔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.7.body.1.step.step2.text": "關閉麵蓋，並將把手下壓以鎖紧麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.7.body.1.step.step3.text": "點擊 [btn:Seal] 按鍵，並等待機器完成工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.section_title": "操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.1.text": "6.3 如何延長密封時間",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.2.text": "若需延長密封時間，需在操作前點擊 [btn:Extend Seal Time] 按鍵，使该按鍵指示燈點亮。延長時間設置將持續生效。若要恢復默認密封時間，請在下一次操作前再次點擊该按鍵。當機器進入休眠或斷電重新開機，密封時間將会恢復默認設置。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.text": "啟用 Extend Seal Time 功能時，將暫時禁用智能密封調節功能，連續工作時每次工作間隔需大於 20s，並打開麵蓋以便機器散熱。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.title": "注意",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.section_title": "操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.1.text": "6.4 如何使用真空密封功能",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.2.text": "**真空密封固體物品：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step1.text": "將袋口放入真空腔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step2.text": "關閉麵蓋，並下壓把手以鎖紧麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step3.text": "點擊 [btn:Vac Mode] 按鍵選擇模式：**Normal** 或 **Gentle**。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step4.text": "點擊 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 按鍵啟動工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step5.text": "若需終止工作，請點擊 [btn:Stop] 按鍵。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.4.text": "在採用 Gentle 模式封裝貴重物品前，建議先採用其它物品嘗試真空後的壓缩程度是否滿足需求，以免壓碎物品。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.5.text": "**真空密封液體：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step1.text": "保持袋子直立，確保液體液麵始終低於發熱器，液體与袋口之間建議留出 7 inch（18 cm）的空間。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step2.text": "將袋口放入真空腔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step3.text": "關閉麵蓋，並下壓把手以鎖紧麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step4.text": "點擊 [btn:Vac Mode] 按鍵選擇 **Liquid** 模式。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step5.text": "點擊 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 按鍵啟動工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.section_title": "操作指引（續）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.1.text": "6.5 如何使用手動真空",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.2.text": "**方法一（在自動真空過程中切換至 Pulse Vac 模式）：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step1.text": "長按 [btn:Pulse Vac] 按鍵進行真空抽氣。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step2.text": "鬆開按鍵則暫停抽氣。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step3.text": "達到所需真空狀態後，點擊 [btn:Seal] 按鍵進行密封。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.4.text": "**方法二（直接使用 Pulse Vac 模式）：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step1.text": "將袋口放入真空腔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step2.text": "關閉麵蓋，並下壓把手以鎖紧麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step3.text": "長按 [btn:Pulse Vac] 按鍵進行真空抽氣。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step4.text": "鬆開按鍵則暫停抽氣。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step5.text": "達到所需真空狀態後，點擊 [btn:Seal] 按鍵進行密封。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.6.text": "在手動真空過程中，長按按鍵抽氣，鬆開暫停，此時会處於保壓的狀態。若 10 秒內不進行再次操作，機器將自動釋放壓力，並退出手動抽氣模式。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.section_title": "操作指引（續）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.1.text": "6.6 真空軟管用法",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.2.body.1.item.1": "對梅森罐適配器和带閥门拉鏈袋抽真空時，圓形吸嘴採用方向1。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.2.body.1.item.2": "對真空罐和瓶塞抽真空時，根據抽氣口大小選擇方向1或2。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.2.body.1.item.3": "真空軟管扁形吸嘴3用於連接機器麵蓋上的外抽氣口3。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.3.text": "6.7 如何抽梅森罐",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step1.text": "閉合機器麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step2.text": "將罐蓋放到梅森罐罐口，不需擰上螺紋蓋（如有）。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step3.text": "將適配器安裝到梅森罐上。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step4.text": "將真空軟管扁形吸嘴插入機器麵蓋上的外抽氣孔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step5.text": "壓下把手以鎖紧麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step6.text": "點擊 [btn:Accessories] 按鍵，選擇 **Mason Jar**。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step7.text": "將真空軟管圓形吸嘴覆蓋適配器的抽氣孔，並用手輕微按壓住。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step8.text": "點擊 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 按鍵啟動工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step9.text": "工作結束，取下真空軟管及適配器。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.section_title": "操作指引（附件使用）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.1.text": "6.8 如何抽真空罐",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step1.text": "操作前，請確認真空罐与本機真空軟管兼容。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step2.text": "確認真空罐處於可抽真空（Vacuum）的狀態。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step3.text": "將真空軟管扁形吸嘴插入機器麵蓋上的外抽氣孔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step4.text": "壓下把手以鎖紧麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step5.text": "點擊 [btn:Accessories] 按鍵，選擇 **Canister**。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step6.text": "將真空軟管圓形吸嘴覆蓋真空罐抽氣閥的抽氣孔，並用手輕微壓住。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step7.text": "點擊 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 按鍵啟動工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step8.text": "工作結束，取下真空軟管。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.section_title": "操作指引（附件使用）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.1.text": "6.9 如何醃製",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step1.text": "將食物覆蓋醬料，並放到真空罐中。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step2.text": "確認真空罐處於可以抽真空（Vacuum）的狀態。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step3.text": "將真空軟管扁形吸嘴插入機器麵蓋上的外抽氣孔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step4.text": "將真空軟管圓形吸嘴插入抽氣閥的抽氣孔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step5.text": "壓下把手以鎖紧麵蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step6.text": "點擊 [btn:Accessories] 按鍵，選擇 **Canister**。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step7.text": "點擊 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 啟動工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step8.text": "工作結束，取下真空軟管。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.section_title": "操作指引（續）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.block.1.text": "6.10 卷袋倉操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.block.2.item.1": "本機器可以同時放置兩卷卷袋（例如：兩卷小於等於 20 feet/6m 長的卷袋）。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.block.2.item.2": "若放置單卷袋，則最長可放置 50 feet（15m）長。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.block.2.item.3": "卷袋倉可容納 12 inch（300mm）以下寬度的卷袋。底部為寬度在 8 inch（200mm）以下的卷袋設計了專用放置槽。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.section_title": "操作指引（續）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.1": "故障现象",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.2": "可能原因",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.3": "解決方案",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.1": "**不能開機**",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.2": "電源線未正確插入電源插座",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.3": "確保電源線已正確插入。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.2.cell.1": "電源線破裂或損壞",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.2.cell.2": "斷電檢查電源線，如有損壞請諮詢專業人员更換。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.3.cell.1": "控製板或麵板排線端子鬆脫",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.3.cell.2": "請諮詢專業人员進行維修。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.1": "**抽氣不乾净**",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.2": "袋子開口未全部在密封圈內",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.3": "確保袋子的開口全部在下真空腔密封圈內。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.1": "使用了非紋路真空袋",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.2": "確保使用带有紋路的真空袋。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.1": "密封圈破損、翻起或安裝不正確",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.2": "檢查密封圈狀態並正確安裝。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.1": "袋子破損或有針孔",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.2": "更換新的真空袋。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.8.cell.1": "袋口有異物導致密封不完整",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.8.cell.2": "將袋口清潔乾净後再試。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.9.cell.1": "熱封時間過長導致溫度過高",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.9.cell.2": "打開麵蓋，静置冷却一段時間再使用。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.10.cell.1": "**不能密封或密封效果不理想**",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.10.cell.2": "袋口没有正確放到發熱器上",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.10.cell.3": "重新放置袋口，確保平整跨過發熱器。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.11.cell.1": "密封區域有水分、颗粒或碎片",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.11.cell.2": "清潔密封區域後重試。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.12.cell.1": "密封壓條未安裝",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.12.cell.2": "安裝密封壓條。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.13.cell.1": "默認密封時間不足",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.13.cell.2": "點擊 [btn:Extend Seal Time] 延長密封時間後重試。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.14.cell.1": "**真空密封後袋子漏氣**",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.14.cell.2": "高溫膠布破損或脫落",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.14.cell.3": "及時替換高溫膠布。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.15.cell.1": "發熱溫度異常導致袋子融化或密封不充分",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.15.cell.2": "參考抽氣不乾净和不能密封的解決方案。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.16.cell.1": "锋利物品刺穿袋子",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.16.cell.2": "用紙巾或防刺穿片包裹锋利邊缘，使用新袋重試。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.2.text": "一些水果和蔬菜在包裝前如果没有正確地焯熟，或者熱的食物，会釋放氣體，導致真空袋没有收紧，此類情况属於正常表现，不属於漏氣。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.2.title": "提示",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.3.text": "若以上故障排除方案均無法解決問題，請聯繫客服指引解決，請不要擅自拆卸機器。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.section_title": "故障排除",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.header.1": "故障现象",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.header.2": "可能原因",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.header.3": "解決方案",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.1.cell.1": "**Accessories 模式無法抽氣**",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.1.cell.2": "真空軟管扁形吸嘴未完全插入外抽氣孔",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.1.cell.3": "用力旋轉下壓扁形吸嘴，使其完全插入。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.2.cell.1": "麵蓋把手未下壓鎖紧",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.2.cell.2": "下壓把手以鎖紧麵蓋後重試。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.3.cell.1": "密封圈或真空腔上有異物",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.3.cell.2": "打開麵蓋清除異物，閉蓋重試。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.4.cell.1": "**错误報警（蜂鳴聲長鳴 + 指示燈快閃）**",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.4.cell.2": "按下 Vac&Seal/Start 或 Seal 後報警",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.4.cell.3": "檢查麵蓋是否閉合，把手是否已下壓鎖紧。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.5.cell.1": "真空工作過程中連續蜂鳴",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.block.1.row.5.cell.2": "機器無法達到目標壓力，檢查把手鎖紧及袋子是否破損，更換新袋重試。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page2.section_title": "故障排除（附件与報警）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.1.text": "如因特殊原因，導致液體進入機器內部的處理方案",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.2.text": "**液體進入真空腔中：**",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.3.step.step1.text": "立即關閉電源，等待至少 5 分鐘，讓機器發熱器冷却。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.3.step.step2.text": "將液體槽取出，並清理擦乾液體。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.3.step.step3.text": "將真空腔中的液體擦乾。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.3.step.step4.text": "將機器底部铺墊廚房紙或托盤，重新通電。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.3.step.step5.text": "合上麵蓋，長按 [btn:Pulse Vac] 按鍵抽氣 20 秒，然後點擊 [btn:Stop] 排氣，重復 5 次，讓內部管道的液體排出。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.3.step.step6.text": "打開麵蓋，在機器底部铺墊廚房紙或托盤，將機器放置於通風處晾乾 48 小時，期間不要翻倒機器。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.4.text": "**液體進入發熱器：**",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.5.step.step1.text": "請勿翻倒機器，關閉電源，等待 10 分鐘，讓發熱器冷却及內部液體排出。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.5.step.step2.text": "清理和擦乾機器接水盤、真空腔、底部的液體。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.5.step.step3.text": "打開麵蓋，在機器底部铺墊廚房紙或托盤，將機器放置於通風處晾乾 24 小時，期間不要翻倒機器。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.5.step.step4.text": "將機器底部铺墊廚房紙或托盤，重新通電。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.5.step.step5.text": "合上麵蓋，長按 [btn:Pulse Vac] 按鍵抽氣 20 秒，然後點擊 [btn:Stop] 排氣，重復 5 次，讓內部管道的液體排出。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.5.step.step6.text": "打開麵蓋，在機器底部铺墊廚房紙或托盤，將機器放置於通風處晾乾 48 小時，期間不要翻倒機器。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.6.text": "如果長期不清潔，內部管道可能会堵塞，影響抽氣性能，此時請聯繫售後進行管道更換。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.block.6.title": "注意",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page3.section_title": "故障排除（續）",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.1": "確保使用機器的工作臺平整、乾净、乾燥。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.2": "在不使用機器時請不要將機器鎖扣鎖上，以防密封圈被長時間挤壓，影響功能。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.3": "需每周一次對機器的密封圈、密封壓條、發熱器、液體槽、真空腔進行清潔。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.4": "發熱器和密封壓條在工作後会殘留高溫，請待機器冷却後再進行保養。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.5": "清潔前拔下機器電源。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.6": "請採用軟毛刷清潔密封圈、密封壓條、發熱器、液體槽、真空腔、真空軟管。避免採用硬毛刷，以免損壞機器。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.7": "每天工作結束後，取出液體槽清潔擦乾，並用濕毛巾或紙巾清理真空腔內殘留的碎屑、灰塵。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.8": "每次工作結束後，檢查密封圈是否已經變形嚴重，高溫膠布是否已經破損/脫落，如有，則請及時替換。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.item.9": "液體槽和真空軟管不支持高溫清潔，如洗碗機清潔。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.section_title": "維護保養",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.1.text": "真空包裝是通過去除密封容器中的大部分空氣来延長食品的壽命，並防止空氣回流到密封容器中，從而減少氧化。真空包裝有助於保持風味和整體質量。它還有助於抑製好氧微生物的生長，在某些條件下可能的现象有：",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "**霉菌** — 霉菌在低氧環境下無法繁殖，真空包裝能够抑製霉菌的繁殖。",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "**酵母菌** — 酵母需要水、糖和中等溫度才能繁殖，可以在有空氣或無空氣的情况下生存。減緩酵母的生長需要冷藏，冷凍則可以有效抑製。",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.2.item.3": "**細菌** — 導致難聞的氣味、變色或變柔軟。在適當的條件下，肉毒梭菌可以在没有空氣的情况下生長，且無法通過氣味或味道檢测到。",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.3.text": "与任何其他儲存方式一樣，在食用前檢查食品是否變質是很重要的。在 -4°C 或更低溫度下，可以显著減少微生物的生長。對於長期儲存，建議進行真空封裝後保持冷凍。",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.4.text": "真空包裝不能代替冷藏或冷凍。任何需要冷藏的易腐食品在真空包裝後仍必須保持冷藏或冷凍。",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.4.title": "NOTICE",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.5.text": "存儲指南",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.6.item.1": "蔬菜在真空包裝前需要先焯水。將蔬菜放入沸水中煮熟，然後浸入冷水中，最後用毛巾吸乾水分再進行真空包裝。",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.6.item.2": "十字花科蔬菜（花椰菜、芽菜、卷心菜等）在儲存過程中会自然排放氣體，煮熟、真空封裝後建議存放在冰箱里。",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.block.6.item.3": "切忌真空儲存大蒜或蘑菇等真菌食品。抽真空後会產生有害物質，食用会影響健康。",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.page.page1.section_title": "真空包裝特性",
